               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270913-310-cd1726" type="crimeDate">11th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-310-off1725 t18270913-310-cd1726"></join>, 1 watch, value 3l.; 1 chain, value 1l., and 2 keys, value 5s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18270913-310-victim2350" type="victimName">
                        George 
                        Russell
                     <interp inst="t18270913-310-victim2350" type="surname" value="Russell"></interp>
